    {
      "title": "haphazard<div class=\"pl-2 flex-1 text-textSecondary text-xl font-serif\">(adj.)</div>",
      "html": "<p>“characterized by randomness, chance, accidental,” 1670年代，源自名词意为“偶然，意外”（1570年代），来自于 <a title=\"Etymology, meaning and definition of hap \" class=\"crossreference notranslate\" href=\"/cn/word/hap\">hap</a>（名词）“机会，运气” + <a title=\"Etymology, meaning and definition of hazard \" class=\"crossreference notranslate\" href=\"/cn/word/hazard\">hazard</a>（名词）“风险，危险，危险”。相关词汇： <i class=\"foreign notranslate\">Haphazardly</i>。</p>"
